  "detailed_description": "<strong>If you would like the English version, please add it to your wishlist. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/840708109a23bbcee183549899c8849a.poster.avif?t=1751480057\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/840708109a23bbcee183549899c8849a.webm?t=1751480057\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/840708109a23bbcee183549899c8849a.mp4?t=1751480057\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Immerse yourself in a world of bittersweet romance!<br><br>Experience a young girl's tale of pure love, brought to life through stunning visuals and endearing characters. This poignant story will captivate your heart and leave a lasting impression.<br><br>●Story<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/579b71736bf793c38326d66ea3a29db6.avif?t=1751480057\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>\"--I'm not human. They call me a devil.\"<br><br>The story begins with a shocking confession between Remi, a boy who works as a jewelry engineer who was raised by demons, and Lazriel, a girl who loses her memory.<br>She follows Remi's guidance and begins to live her peaceful life, but soon she is plagued by inexplicable dreams. In her dream, she was called Ilsa and was a devoted believer with deep faith in the Archangel.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/bf4764f3ee2a8b48da84f7532ae543fe.avif?t=1751480057\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>\"You're lying! Pretending that the devil exists!\"<br><br>People doubt the existence of witches, and an insanity trial begins.<br>A drama about a girl's crazy pure love that is finally revealed as innocent people are executed due to false charges.<br><br>\"Even though I know this love is forbidden...\"<br><br>And you will know the truth.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/acdd6dad69469afaa4e4d533865168d3.avif?t=1751480057\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br>●Character<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/7d760fe783f05f5151474f9aa1fe1737.avif?t=1751480057\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/43243d4b66f6a8a4804f683b3a4e1e97.avif?t=1751480057\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/b7cd1ce56b73002726df645bd45555cd.avif?t=1751480057\" width=200 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/c730da86f45a08ff4bafd81e6a38f428.avif?t=1751480057\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2818450/extras/06c7b88dc2e2bd952add8b9828f54829.avif?t=1751480057\" width=200 height=200 /></span><br><br>Get ready to enjoy a story woven by wonderful characters!",
